subject: Lead Time Microservice
description:
As a project manager, I would like to view the lead time of a user story so that I can understand the performance of a team  
  
Acceptance Criteria :   
1) Given I send a request with a Project ID and User Story ID, then compute and return the Lead time in JSON format so that I may know the lead time of a user story

subject: Lead time Microservice Status messages
description:
As a project manager, I would like to get specific error codes with specific error messages when data validation fails so that I may know when I input the wrong data  
  
Acceptance Criteria :   
Given a request is send to lead time micro service, then return : 200 Status code when there is a success response, or 401 when authorisation token is invalid, or 404 when Project ID does not exist, or 404 when user story is not found so that I may know when there is an issue.

subject: Cycle Time Microservice
description: As a project manager, I would like to view the cycle time of a user story so that I can understand the performance and efficiency of a team to identify issues

subject: Throughput Microservice
description: As a project manager, I would like to view the throughput of a user story so that I can understand the performance and efficiency of a team to identify any bottlenecks and issues of the team
